{"tid":2184867,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冀年底前關閉所有美大學孔子學院 蓬佩奧：中國的挑戰有異於冷戰年代","createTime":"2020-09-02T01:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T01:54:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aad0a197d2dc1b1bd00f97e7757fcaa43978e965","tid":2184867,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧接受 Fox Business News 訪問，指由中國政府資助的孔子學院試圖從美國大專院校中招募間諜及其協作者，並認為院校應察覺到此問題。他坦言：「我希望能在今年年底之前，將它們（孔子學院）全部關閉。」美國國務院上月中 (14/8) 已宣佈，要求孔子學院註冊為「外交使團 (Foreign Mission)」，蓬佩奧當時形容該機構為「推進北京的全球宣傳和惡性影響的實體」。東岸地區首席外交官 David Stilwell 也在當時要求大學應「認真仔細」了解孔子學院在院校所做的一切。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%86%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%AD%94%E5%AD%90%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E6%9C%89%E7%95%B0%E6%96%BC%E5%86%B7%E6%88%B0%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AD%2594%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258C%2591%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2595%25B0%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A3%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=cc03f8b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AD%2594%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258C%25